{
  "stem": "11272.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, I had to run away from home-- first to my aunt and uncle in, in Vari where I brought up to you that my aunt, and uncle, and their children all perished in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had-- it was quite a, a long way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, I had no car, no bicycle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had to hitch a ride here and there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to go to Munkacs, and from there to Beregsaz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from Beregsaz, I walked all the way to Vari.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they, they--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--would have killed me for sure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I came back, they found out after a while that I came-- you know, that I was back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they attacked me again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my brother Sam and I were going to take care of our cow that was grazing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had some straw there and hay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were going to rake it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and he had a pitchfork.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had a rake.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they attacked us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And fortunately, we made our stand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We run to a small bridge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we made our stand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We left all of them bleeding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we ran away again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I did this one more time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then I finally had to-- disappeared from the area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I left and went to the capital of Hungary, Budapest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to Lavik to-- where we had an aunt and uncle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Our uncle in Lavik had, I believe, seven or eight kids.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one of them is still alive-- the only one that survived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And our aunt had 13 children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And only one survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was trapped in Russia for about 28 years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when he finally came out to Israel, he got sick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he died there.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
